songs.title: Never Bother Looking Back
songs.lyrics:
It felt real nice

I didn't think twice

It felt real good

Like I knew it would

And I don't care, and I don't mind

If I'm unfair or you're unkind

'Cause right now I'm still kickin' back

It doesn't matter, I never bother

Looking back

It felt real fine

It was all mine

It's not too strong

It didn't last for long

And I don't care, and I don't mind

If I'm unfair or you're unkind

'Cause right now Im still kickin' back

It doesn't matter, I never bother

Looking back

It felt real good

Like I knew it should

It felt so good

Like I knew it would

And I don't care, and I don't mind

If I'm unfair or you're unkind

'Cause right now I'm still kickin' back

It doesn't matter, I never bother

Looking back
